data:
select
    url,
    earliest_time_trended,
    latest_time_trended,
    seconds_trending / 60.0 / 60.0 as hours_trending
from trending_articles
order by 3 desc

select * from (select
    url,
    earliest_time_trended,
    latest_time_trended,
    seconds_trending / 60.0 / 60.0 as hours_trending
from trending_articles
order by 3 desc) where hours_trending < 1000

select median(hours_trending) as median_hours_trending from (select
    url,
    earliest_time_trended,
    latest_time_trended,
    seconds_trending / 60.0 / 60.0 as hours_trending
from trending_articles
order by 3 desc)
